      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[New: Browse from — pick one of your machines and browse the internet from its location. Name each machine's place, offer machines to your other devices, all from the menu bar.]]></description>
