      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.7.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[Your Mac can now browse from another of your machines: pick one and both your connection and your lookups come from its location. Also hardens the connection path between your device and the machine you picked.]]></description>
