      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.6.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[Browsing from another of your machines now moves name lookups there too, so location checks see the machine you picked. Linux agents only; no Mac app changes.]]></description>
