      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[Linux agents can now carry another of your devices' internet connection — groundwork for Browse From (pick a country by picking a machine). No Mac app changes.]]></description>
      <enclosure url="https://github.com/thecloudstation/connect-releases/releases/download/v1.5.0/CloudStationConnect-1.5.0.zip"
